#. <section class="sutta" id="an6.117"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.117:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6"

#. </p><p>
#. VAR: 12. Sāmaññavagga → vaggāsaṅgahitā suttantā (s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an6.117:0.2"
msgid "12. Sāmaññavagga"
msgstr "12. The Ascetic Life"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.117:0.3"
msgid "117. Kāyānupassīsutta"
msgstr "117. Observing the Body"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an6.117:1.1"
msgid "“Cha, bhikkhave, dhamme appahāya abhabbo kāye kāyānupassī viharituṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, without giving up these six qualities you can’t meditate "
"observing an aspect of the body."

msgctxt "an6.117:1.2"
msgid "Katame cha?"
msgstr "What six?"

msgctxt "an6.117:1.3"
msgid ""
"Kammārāmataṃ, bhassārāmataṃ, niddārāmataṃ, saṅgaṇikārāmataṃ, indriyesu "
"aguttadvārataṃ, bhojane amattaññutaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Relishing work, talk, sleep, and company, not guarding the sense doors, and "
"eating too much."

msgctxt "an6.117:1.4"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, cha dhamme appahāya abhabbo kāye kāyānupassī viharituṃ."
msgstr ""
"Without giving up these six qualities you can’t meditate observing an aspect "
"of the body."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.450"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an6.117:2.1"
msgid "Cha, bhikkhave, dhamme pahāya bhabbo kāye kāyānupassī viharituṃ."
msgstr ""
"But after giving up these six qualities you can meditate observing an aspect "
"of the body."

msgctxt "an6.117:2.2"
msgid "Katame cha?"
msgstr "What six?"

msgctxt "an6.117:2.3"
msgid ""
"Kammārāmataṃ, bhassārāmataṃ, niddārāmataṃ, saṅgaṇikārāmataṃ, indriyesu "
"aguttadvārataṃ, bhojane amattaññutaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Relishing work, talk, sleep, and company, not guarding the sense doors, and "
"eating too much."

msgctxt "an6.117:2.4"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, cha dhamme pahāya bhabbo kāye kāyānupassī viharitun”ti."
msgstr ""
"After giving up these six qualities you can meditate observing an aspect of "
"the body.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.117:2.5"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
